title: How many packages per wallet on 2nd INO?
body:
Dear Community

We’d like to go through a governance vote prior to 2nd INO-Lime Pre-sale,

Gvnc Vote: Limit the INO packages per wallet by

1. 1 package per wallet
2. 2 packages per wallet
3. 3 packages per wallet

Please stay with us, we’ll try our best to incorporate your voices in the community channel.

Vote will start Friday 03:00 UTC and end Saturday 03:00 UTC.

We’ll deliver more news on Lime Odyssey M with the voting result.
author: 0xe38526Dbe387FDaFaD76cAF9dEEAd525842a2a88
